<main class="govuk-main-wrapper" id="content" role="main">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
            <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">
                Submit learner data
            </h1>

            <p class="govuk-body-l">This service is for training providers that receive funding directly from the Education and Skills Funding Agency.</p>

            <p>Use this service to validate and submit:</p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>Individualised learner records (ILR)</li>
                <li>Earnings adjustment statements (EAS)</li>
                <li>ESFA supplementary data - including ESF (European Social Fund)</li>
                <li>Funding claims</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                You can also view and download reports for data you’ve submitted.
            </p>

            <a href="/ilr-submission" class="govuk-button govuk-button--start" id="signin" >Sign in</a>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>
            <p>You will need:</p>

            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>Your IdAMS (Information Management Services system) login details</li>
                <li>If you’re submitting ILR or EAS data, an XML or Zip file to upload</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

